{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>網上報稅教學2026｜8個扣稅方法助你節省近$10000、寛限期多1個月｜稅務局今日（4日）已發出277萬份2025/26年度的個別人士報税表，市民必須在6月4日</p><p>網上報稅教學2026｜8大慳稅位 扣超過$10000元稅額！</p><p>根據稅務局資訊，2025/26年度的個別人士報税表已於2026年5月4日寄出，納税人須於報税表發出日期起的1個月內(即2026年6月4日或以前)妥及交回報税表，遲報稅分分鐘而被罰$10000元！改用網上報稅的方式就可延長1個月交表寛限期，記得盡快填表了。下面有圖表可看到各種個人免稅額，快看看那個合用、不要填漏！👇🏻</p><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128247894374092800503198.png/kNvaPQazByhPjuse_faEPjrIGEHZTDv3YPQiq2D0Iqs\"><p>MPF／個人進修／慈善捐款項目都可以扣稅\n即睇8個慳稅位，扣超過$10000元稅額！</p><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230250467299328427150.jpeg/S3owXFUEsf6Y7iQUps6H9I6V17IYczqEu2f08btn9PE\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230252728160256917380.jpeg/2yV1EkB51S8mY3bxZOWFMtB87PPv3cwtzQ5ZP80OWT8\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230254951272448984560.jpeg/Gs_HqcXyfXEvv0J20SXsZL4qcBOIH0l6vTJlDL0yZQw\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230257409265664084219.jpeg/6iCG4dVQuDziXvlHwb-BgML8WQ97hsYN20gkwdtIJME\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230259611406336852794.jpeg/KZ3wNznoSVgAZjbJeUREhUP3U1RMrMro5s2tNObNrTQ\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230250211446784763810.jpeg/LqeMGGSC-7EHFaeduhNFfSAVownZSCwy_kWErv5FhK4\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230252682022912830721.jpeg/KI38IpqDqABXHimI64NEKLW-2IqgApSEGppe-xqaXvs\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230255035158528691502.jpeg/yipY7N4NqFPUj7Vx2bjUbMiP2PknGrtFvkXN7r5Fze4\"><p>至於點樣網上報稅呢？首先最好安裝「智方便」流動應用程式，並開通你的「智方便＋」資格，才能夠在GovHK 香港政府一站通內使用「稅務易」網上報稅。</p><p>👇👇要使用「報稅易」，你必須先申請「智方便+」\n以下為申請步驟、24個可用「智方便」網上申請公營服務列表👇👇</p><p>👍如已持有「智方便+」可跳到下一項👍</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320851695865856046852.jpeg/nwXuM0yPZWpBKNGAigDbjjtGY_9X5mZhrd9bCK3fWwg\" alt=\"申請「智方便+」\n3分鐘完成申請步驟\"><figcaption>申請「智方便+」\n3分鐘完成申請步驟</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320854032224256172653.jpeg/5fhbcJqtjZ7CWVYqxzArM2I9Xq-ZAsV68vV2w_L1dsM\" alt=\"步驟1\t前往就近郵政局\"><figcaption>步驟1\t前往就近郵政局</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320856813178880812796.jpeg/_4-Jnyy9ZPvqXh_BJrCYHFsT7GhY_OOcbEcExGxHBMQ\" alt=\"步驟2\t排隊登記\"><figcaption>步驟2\t排隊登記</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320859325698048340829.jpeg/UMUaSia41TjA1N-1popMI1CqxqCAjRR6rF2Di6xdg4s\" alt=\"（pic22）\n步驟3\tScan QR code\"><figcaption>（pic22）\n步驟3\tScan QR code</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320861611724800806957.jpeg/3vIv_dro437ntFuvA4580qpUgLUsx8vN99srj_fbK48\" alt=\"步驟4\t身份證認證\"><figcaption>步驟4\t身份證認證</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320863813865472051364.jpeg/vYUq4fpswBSo2iZ9VheChzwogSoV70avQQqZGkEKmRo\" alt=\"步驟5\t驗證手機\"><figcaption>步驟5\t驗證手機</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320866053754880103659.jpeg/H7TeToEszsteIxvh8ITCoYKPP2LAsQqQr-L6_K_i-vw\" alt=\"步驟6\t驗證Email\"><figcaption>步驟6\t驗證Email</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320868562079744018276.jpeg/THeWm2_eS2zoTA19NZmdpfdI2Ze_OY85rfLg5q3y4OY\" alt=\"步驟7\t完成登記\"><figcaption>步驟7\t完成登記</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320870944575488920876.jpeg/osj1he-Bkt1AUny4FELRMdIckcHcaUpQutPpFrrT6RY\" alt=\"網上申請24種政府服務\n所需認證\n（智方便 或 智方便+）\"><figcaption>網上申請24種政府服務\n所需認證\n（智方便 或 智方便+）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320873494843392278951.jpeg/RtD5Ak-Mz3BR5j53_iAs-b1yHZeWWWs6qgG6M6oBujM\" alt=\"路政署\"><figcaption>路政署</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320851205132288081792.jpeg/WH6YfEIpYQ679NTLSU95_KYCwQ1Qdh1u_E61SvxOtUo\" alt=\"香港天文台\"><figcaption>香港天文台</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320853755400192540627.jpeg/h-kVG8hPFPPuzywnU5pWWVoP1yuf-A_69UCfnvVAn54\" alt=\"香港郵政\"><figcaption>香港郵政</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320856091758592179246.jpeg/p9bR2HnXF-hyh5woTXbmDDKZ5msKECxbLtMKMy7TCjM\" alt=\"房屋委員會\"><figcaption>房屋委員會</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320858646220800826790.jpeg/JsXwRZVwPKbEoPZrsu2FUoZ6TpS_m3wi59-7K-ffuys\" alt=\"稅務局\"><figcaption>稅務局</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320861011939328014275.jpeg/oMLprQ8OGalv2Haqyi-YEq0BpgA87QsDwZN2JMGTdiQ\" alt=\"勞工處\"><figcaption>勞工處</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320863348297728346971.jpeg/wD6Ko5SOoSLXR26tFZeUZA7zeVhzKLcWopFpvaKRab0\" alt=\"政府資訊科技總監辦公室\"><figcaption>政府資訊科技總監辦公室</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320865785319424691837.jpeg/nBfSp9vJXZu7zY3Sr-D5o31Jp0rxV4GuAeBpoQHgaaE\" alt=\"政府資訊科技總監辦公室\"><figcaption>政府資訊科技總監辦公室</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320868247506944051279.jpeg/J5vgI9QRcEcd9rsBRmRfxxzxBiRSEGv-3iMOA94jDgM\" alt=\"差餉物業估價署\"><figcaption>差餉物業估價署</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320870424481792724360.jpeg/YgkYUt7dWAWaDqCkMay1ETOtt6GVW40Iepgak3qYGpM\" alt=\"運輸署\"><figcaption>運輸署</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320873129938944035746.jpeg/EpjdZDx-zJR8mwPNFJHh0KSgNxtKnsMSycg1EcnINRE\" alt=\"運輸署\"><figcaption>運輸署</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210122/429320835254194176921473.jpeg/-9_W549-idwpefnFiT3yPQuae5_B6xI8NzYpnjc2KZ4\" alt=\"在職家庭及學生資助事務處學生資助處\"><figcaption>在職家庭及學生資助事務處學生資助處</figcaption></figure><p>智方便 3分鐘開戶網上續車牌、報稅24項政府服務</p><p>2026網上報稅教學⬇</p><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263366448517120928074.jpeg/JQUdwwLRbamMLfvIdgkm61hS4cj91DW7JFWlOiRVpTo\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263369883783168726905.jpeg/IQWQIm-sNOgW4KTC5S8WNDsqERLqMw55T0LYsE9C2LA\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263372962533376542097.jpeg/eM2vnZC_9IQkcaF49g0hvyB7gPk3vYYReX6mBHl-pgQ\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263375546355712936128.jpeg/tA8y2-VntoG2DkjnvqBpF8uoDZGGErPBleRf9ZXkX_U\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263377974988800314708.jpeg/Z5Go7m4MJ1OGO1FZyEh65T_ijuoVlIiH4BYFuOAWBbg\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263366444322816968207.jpeg/PQH0he0FkYD6gj9dtKTRKVyQFbJNxellN0OIKTdDiCk\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263369774731264402815.jpeg/GyOUtshx5qu5tZJggY_J8j6XrMY0x1csIq1mSiKtZko\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263372547297280783450.jpeg/PKP_d5Jlgdk8VWIIXyOH3oPlqhAw4OAQWqTL5Fqky-Q\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263374921404416407839.jpeg/U-_v4_3Y8vr_5-dVZgVvra5VwUoVJviKNNH4LjTR-C4\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263377530392576167984.jpeg/mTFzmbjehGUgY3IyBoXg_f8FXtqXosdKgrpwvIK6cLw\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263366335270912105369.jpeg/6IlAv54xHRckQTlrE1xHr4FTnggFttHwkO6fRZDun0U\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263370307407872518603.jpeg/Gdhv_R3mnJU8LNEchBqMhDl66iC0qsiN0O3yEtDt8hI\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128263372903813120502389.jpeg/o4XINl9UjZFiQT5DMzATLH0VSUzRGYNODE3dUgxN3VI\"><p>智方便登入稅務易⬇</p><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230141138571264201938.jpeg/C5Mc-gqaaEGtNIWS6DIcvLQvpwPdDPQOZhifp2YYn6c\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128264180755861504810395.jpeg/QzAiDC4e6xe81Shneqsh3pKAPU2Axx7OhRBmw4UQZsM\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230146369130496927463.jpeg/wd2cdTfIk84eWK527y4F3cBcscexHCjOhq2dKIatnSg\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230148520939520859104.jpeg/aNbpw93DqMpLQZwMVHCYFMdw3ltYMXdY3CHvU9wh71M\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230151247368192631492.jpeg/dpdcjov9ueHENEwphhT9RoyC3cKgWb7S4sBuzOLAbsw\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20240506/864230140211630080697084.jpeg/UrU6XIu8CQIoKuJYteZ5CD27rL8qe-Zca8UBqmvFAao\"><p>2026/27年度免稅額、扣除額已作出調整（見下表）\n但留意我們今次要提交的是2025/26年個人報稅單</p><p>．基本及單親免稅額由13.2萬元增至14.5萬元</p><p>．已婚人士免稅額由26.4萬元增至29萬元</p><p>．子女免稅額及額外子女免稅額由13萬元增加至14萬元</p><p>．供養60歲或以上父母或祖父母的免稅額由5萬元增加至5.5萬元</p><p>．供養55至59歲的父母或祖父母的免稅額，由2.5萬元增至2.75萬元</p><p>．父母或祖父母入住合資格院舍、長者住宿照顧開支的扣除上限由10萬元增加至11萬元</p><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260505/1128270197031964672734165.png/RO2YJGWCzWR_yYpbRkekyzx87bCedV7FXPyt31z8rd8\"></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-05T07:32:03.245520+00:00","quality":{"score":2,"chars":966,"images":50,"source":"HK01 熱話","fallback":"none"}}